Cancellable event created by the DropHeads plugin when a behead message is sent.

  • Constructor Details

    • BeheadMessageEvent

      public BeheadMessageEvent(Player recipient, Entity victim, Entity killer, TellrawUtils.Component beheadMessage, boolean isGlobal, boolean isPetDeath)
      Create an BeheadMessageEvent for DropHeads.
      Parameters:
      recipient - the Player being sent the behead message
      victim - the Entity which was beheaded
      killer - the Entity which caused the death of victim, or null if no entity was responsible
      beheadMessage - the message being sent
      isGlobal - whether the behead message is globally announced
      isPetDeath - whether the behead message is for a pet
